{"tid":2198351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Biden: 支持終國加入世貿係天真嘅決定? 唔同意","createTime":"2020-09-11T09:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T16:19:14.000Z","uid":270889,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0a956a853ed5793df7eccb97ce58d54cfea868","tid":2198351,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:45:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BaldingsWorld/status/1304274728668987393?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBaldingsWorld%2Fstatus%2F1304274728668987393%3Fs%3D20&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=634f017f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBaldingsWorld%2Fstatus%2F1304274728668987393%3Fs%3D20&h=d6b4a49e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BaldingsWorld/status/1304274728668987393?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">JAKE TAPPER, CNN:</span><br />\n<em>Let me ask you about China. In 2011 when you were vice president you said, quote, &quot;It is in our self-interest that China continue to prosper.&quot; <br />\nA lot of people think that <span class=\"red\">allowing China into the World Trade Organization</span>, which you supported, extending <span class=\"red\">Most Favored Nation status to China</span>, which you supported, that those steps allowed China to take advantage of the United States by using our own open trade deals against us. <span class=\"red\">Do you think, in retrospect, you were naive about China?</span></em><br />\n你支持終國加入世貿 享有最惠國待遇 令佢地可以搵我地笨<br />\n依家諗返起 會唔會覺得之前對終國嘅取態太天真<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">JOE BIDEN:</span><br />\n<em><span class=\"red\"><strong>No</strong></span>, here is the thing. In the context of that,<span class=\"red\"> we want China to grow</span>. <span class=\"red\">We don't want a war with China.</span> I said to Xi Jinping, you may remember the president wanted me to spend time with him as vice president, he couldn't do it, so I traveled around the world with him.</em><br />\n唔會 我地想終國成長 我地唔想同佢開戰<br />\n<br />\n<em>He asked, why do you keep saying you're a Pacific power?<br />\nI said because we are. We are a Pacific power. If we weren't, you would not be able to have any stability at all.<span class=\"red\"> It's in our interest for China to be stable</span>. <span class=\"red\">It's not in our interest for China to take advantage of us</span>.</em><br />\n終國穩定係符合美國利益<br />\n不過佔我地便宜就唔合美國利益<br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"red\">What has Trump done?</span> He poked his finger in the eye of the allies and embraced every autocrat in the world, we make up 25% of the world economy and we've lost all our friends. The way to keep China in line is to make two things clear. Insist we play by international rules.</em><br />\n侵又做咗D咩 佢令美國失去盟友 佢就同獨裁者fd <br />\n要終國唔亂黎 我地要堅守國際慣例<br />\n(其實片中佢先講錯咗做50%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全個CNN訪問好長 我無睇晒<br />\n有興趣嘅你可以搵黎睇下 佢講嘅two things clear入面第二樣係咩<br />\n話埋比我聽 thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d776e9ba11262026f7d8bb35f0d648ec53c8d9bb","tid":2198351,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.realclearpolitics.com/video/2020/09/10/jake_tapper_in_retrospect_do_you_think_you_were_naive_to_allow_china_into_the_wto_biden_no.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realclearpolitics.com%2Fvideo%2F2020%2F09%2F10%2Fjake_tapper_in_retrospect_do_you_think_you_were_naive_to_allow_china_into_the_wto_biden_no.html&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=fe84c13b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.realclearpolitics.com/video/2020/09/10/jake_tapper_in_retrospect_do_you_think_you_were_naive_to_allow_china_into_the_wto_biden_no.html</a>"},{"pid":"8cef5e8f2b1923e56ec2edfcb4d1d7bb7f142f75","tid":2198351,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB